{{#ifexist:{{{1}}}|{{cat more|{{{1}}}}}}}
{{category explanation|categories, lists or general articles about {{{1}}} by [[:Category:Regions|region]], i.e. by named areas of the earth other than continents or countries}}
{{#ifexist:Category:{{{1}}} by continent|{{see also category|{{{1}}} by continent}}}}
{{#ifexist:Category:{{{1}}} by country|{{see also category|{{{1}}} by country}}}}
<noinclude>
{{doc|content=
This template is for use on categories named as "… by region", to explain how this differs from "… by location".

To use it, enter
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{Region category header|Foo}}</syntaxhighlight>
where Foo is the name of the topic being categorised. For example, on [[:Category:Vertebrates by region]], enter
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{Region category header|vertebrates}}</syntaxhighlight>

[[Category:Category header templates]]
}}
</noinclude>

